{"tid":229433,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 世界上到底有冇人鐘意食三色豆","createTime":"2017-05-04T15:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:01:46.000Z","uid":19769,"like":49,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f47e98ca473a055a222bacf8eaf53d4ffe6c9982","tid":229433,"uid":19769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/225647_4d4064ffbb39bfd208082a513f4ced89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F225647_4d4064ffbb39bfd208082a513f4ced89.jpg&h=46661cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n次次去茶記見到都怕 尤其是啲青豆層衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咬落去個口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議大學生O-Camp輸左食一組人食一包三色豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界上到底有冇人鐘意食三色豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 人間美食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 劣食 狗也不屌"},{"pid":"7adc7041d7e99fd362b219ffd12d13bf07207db1","tid":229433,"uid":71299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"我有個fd好鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a453b13f75a397341b4d207e4b21605e1aa308","tid":229433,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"佢既作用係俾我揀出黎<br />\n分返哂顏色<br />\n就會覺得好舒服<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533fcc7a92cc99238b1d3ae8d85bf9e1e34b2067","tid":229433,"uid":19769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢既作用係俾我揀出黎<br />\n分返哂顏色<br />\n就會覺得好舒服<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockqu